WEBVTT

00:00:00.910 --> 00:00:02.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SILVER LEAF FESTIVAL</b></Default>

00:00:02.620 --> 00:00:04.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:00:07.120 --> 00:00:08.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

00:00:08.789 --> 00:00:09.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How's Akagi?</b></Default>

00:00:10.039 --> 00:00:11.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She seems to be doing better.</b></Default>

00:00:12.289 --> 00:00:14.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They said she'll be okay
with a bit of rest.</b></Default>

00:00:15.449 --> 00:00:16.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kamisato.</b></Default>

00:00:16.539 --> 00:00:18.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I ask
how you feel about Akagi?</b></Default>

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:20.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? Why?</b></Default>

00:00:20.539 --> 00:00:22.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, Akagi is so serious</b></Default>

00:00:22.120 --> 00:00:23.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that it makes you worry, right?</b></Default>

00:00:24.039 --> 00:00:25.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She wants to help people.</b></Default>

00:00:25.410 --> 00:00:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So she's aspiring
to become a nurse.</b></Default>

00:00:27.370 --> 00:00:29.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And she's very active
in volunteer work.</b></Default>

00:00:29.539 --> 00:00:31.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah</b></Default>

00:00:31.910 --> 00:00:34.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although I did think it was
all for appearances at first.</b></Default>

00:00:34.869 --> 00:00:36.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Appearances?</b></Default>

00:00:36.329 --> 00:00:37.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know them</b></Default>

00:00:37.329 --> 00:00:39.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>people that act
like they're doing things</b></Default>

00:00:39.539 --> 00:00:42.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-to dress themselves up...
-[cell phone vibrates]</b></Default>

00:00:42.119 --> 00:00:44.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but in actuality</b></Default>

00:00:44.200 --> 00:00:46.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They brag about their lives
to cover that up.</b></Default>

00:00:46.700 --> 00:00:48.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The type with business cards.</b></Default>

00:00:49.289 --> 00:00:51.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Ikumi is different.</b></Default>

00:00:51.369 --> 00:00:53.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She doesn't do
these things to brag</b></Default>

00:00:53.289 --> 00:00:55.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it's not so she can
get the upper hand.</b></Default>

00:00:55.579 --> 00:00:58.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She really is trying
to be of help for someone.</b></Default>

00:00:59.250 --> 00:01:01.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it's kind of creepy
sometimes.</b></Default>

00:01:02.579 --> 00:01:03.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cell phone vibrates]</b></Default>

00:01:04.409 --> 00:01:06.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Chiharu is bugging me
about coming back</b></Default>

00:01:06.620 --> 00:01:07.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'm gonna leave.</b></Default>

00:01:07.750 --> 00:01:09.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Feel free to do whatever.</b></Default>

00:01:09.620 --> 00:01:11.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I trust you
to watch over Ikumi?</b></Default>

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:14.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Believe me, Kamisato</b></Default>

00:01:14.409 --> 00:01:17.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure Akagi will contact you
like she did earlier.</b></Default>

00:01:17.250 --> 00:01:19.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm asking because
she never calls for help</b></Default>

00:01:19.579 --> 00:01:21.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when she's in real trouble.</b></Default>

00:01:26.750 --> 00:01:28.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:02:34.580 --> 00:02:40.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:02:56.539 --> 00:03:00.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}YOU AND I
WITHIN THE REALM OF MEMORIES</b></Default>

00:03:00.159 --> 00:03:02.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[struggling grunts]</b></Default>

00:03:02.120 --> 00:03:03.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[knock at door]</b></Default>

00:03:04.039 --> 00:03:05.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Akagi, can I come in?</b></Default>

00:03:06.330 --> 00:03:07.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] Yeah.</b></Default>

00:03:11.580 --> 00:03:12.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Want me to help?</b></Default>

00:03:14.620 --> 00:03:17.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or I can call Kamisato back
if you'd like.</b></Default>

00:03:17.659 --> 00:03:19.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's fine. Yes, please.</b></Default>

00:03:20.659 --> 00:03:22.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'm gonna unzip it.</b></Default>

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:25.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:27.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft gasp]</b></Default>

00:03:27.289 --> 00:03:28.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

00:03:29.330 --> 00:03:31.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there anything else
you need help with?</b></Default>

00:03:31.539 --> 00:03:33.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I need any more</b></Default>

00:03:34.159 --> 00:03:36.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna change</b></Default>

00:03:43.250 --> 00:03:44.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] What I saw earlier</b></Default>

00:03:44.949 --> 00:03:46.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that wasn't an illness, was it?</b></Default>

00:03:47.409 --> 00:03:48.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI]{\i1} It's like a ghost story{\i0}</b></Default>

00:03:48.699 --> 00:03:50.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}you'd see on TV{\i0}
{\i1}as a kid, right?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:03:51.039 --> 00:03:53.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}A poltergeist</b></Default>

00:03:53.870 --> 00:03:55.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It happens every so often.</b></Default>

00:03:55.500 --> 00:03:56.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But don't worry about me.</b></Default>

00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:59.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can take care
of fixing it myself.</b></Default>

00:03:59.330 --> 00:04:00.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you know how to fix it</b></Default>

00:04:00.750 --> 00:04:02.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but the problem
hasn't been resolved yet.</b></Default>

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I take it that means
the solution isn't an easy one.</b></Default>

00:04:06.750 --> 00:04:07.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI]You're right.</b></Default>

00:04:07.949 --> 00:04:09.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It isn't easy...</b></Default>

00:04:09.659 --> 00:04:12.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to forget you, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:13.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft gasp]</b></Default>

00:04:15.659 --> 00:04:17.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly, it's quite difficult.</b></Default>

00:04:19.329 --> 00:04:21.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think this has
nothing to do with you?</b></Default>

00:04:21.579 --> 00:04:24.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh... Why am I to blame here?</b></Default>

00:04:24.660 --> 00:04:27.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really don't remember
anything about that day.</b></Default>

00:04:30.329 --> 00:04:33.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was a bit suggestive
and annoying of me.</b></Default>

00:04:33.949 --> 00:04:36.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, why don't we
have a contest?</b></Default>

00:04:36.910 --> 00:04:40.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will I be the one who forgets
about you first, Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:04:40.660 --> 00:04:41.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or will you</b></Default>

00:04:41.910 --> 00:04:44.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>remember what happened
that day before me?</b></Default>

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:46.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I play along</b></Default>

00:04:47.290 --> 00:04:50.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you do manage to remember</b></Default>

00:04:50.750 --> 00:04:53.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:04:54.500 --> 00:04:55.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, you should know</b></Default>

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:58.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>remembering important things
is sort of my specialty.</b></Default>

00:04:58.790 --> 00:05:01.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad
you have the motivation now.</b></Default>

00:05:01.540 --> 00:05:03.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you do end up the winner</b></Default>

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:06.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think I'll have to rely
on the Dreaming tag ever again.</b></Default>

00:05:06.829 --> 00:05:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What kind of logic is that?</b></Default>

00:05:08.579 --> 00:05:10.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you saying you searched
for #Dreaming post</b></Default>

00:05:11.040 --> 00:05:12.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to help people out?</b></Default>

00:05:12.250 --> 00:05:14.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Also, that you can
finally forget about me</b></Default>

00:05:14.449 --> 00:05:16.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and recover
from puberty syndrome?</b></Default>

00:05:17.910 --> 00:05:19.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's why</b></Default>

00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:21.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no matter what you tell me
I should do</b></Default>

00:05:21.449 --> 00:05:22.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just can't stop.</b></Default>

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:25.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs] Well</b></Default>

00:05:25.500 --> 00:05:27.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what do you need me
to do for you?</b></Default>

00:05:27.620 --> 00:05:29.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't have to do anything.</b></Default>

00:05:29.449 --> 00:05:30.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If all goes well</b></Default>

00:05:30.449 --> 00:05:32.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd have forgotten
all about you by that point.</b></Default>

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:36.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, please, from now on</b></Default>

00:05:37.829 --> 00:05:39.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can start right now.</b></Default>

00:05:39.829 --> 00:05:40.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ready?</b></Default>

00:05:41.250 --> 00:05:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go.</b></Default>

00:05:42.370 --> 00:05:43.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:05:45.620 --> 00:05:48.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bye now. I have to get back
to the flea market</b></Default>

00:05:48.199 --> 00:05:49.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-and help the kids.
-Yeah.</b></Default>

00:05:54.790 --> 00:05:55.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANO] Big brother!</b></Default>

00:05:56.410 --> 00:05:58.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:05:59.870 --> 00:06:02.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad I was able to find you.</b></Default>

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:04.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You took so long that everyone
started to get worried.</b></Default>

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:07.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry, Kano. I didn't mean
to trouble everyone.</b></Default>

00:06:07.949 --> 00:06:09.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's fine.</b></Default>

00:06:09.410 --> 00:06:10.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That just now</b></Default>

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:12.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was Ms. Ikumi, wasn't it?</b></Default>

00:06:12.750 --> 00:06:14.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on. Do you know her, Kano?</b></Default>

00:06:14.829 --> 00:06:17.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. I go to the same
high school she went to.</b></Default>

00:06:17.290 --> 00:06:19.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was a short while</b></Default>

00:06:19.620 --> 00:06:22.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when we were preparing
for the sports festival.</b></Default>

00:06:22.079 --> 00:06:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. So what kind of person
was Akagi like in high school?</b></Default>

00:06:25.579 --> 00:06:27.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What kind of person was she?</b></Default>

00:06:27.660 --> 00:06:29.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. Before I answer</b></Default>

00:06:29.699 --> 00:06:32.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>let me contact Kae
and tell her I found you.</b></Default>

00:06:33.199 --> 00:06:35.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until the spring I entered</b></Default>

00:06:35.160 --> 00:06:38.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she was the student council
president at our high school.</b></Default>

00:06:38.160 --> 00:06:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ms. Ikumi was super active
in local volunteer work too.</b></Default>

00:06:41.949 --> 00:06:43.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So she's always been like that.</b></Default>

00:06:43.870 --> 00:06:44.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:06:45.040 --> 00:06:48.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even now, she founded
her own volunteer organization</b></Default>

00:06:48.079 --> 00:06:50.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to assist kids
who refuse to attend class.</b></Default>

00:06:51.410 --> 00:06:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's so like Ms. Ikumi.</b></Default>

00:06:53.370 --> 00:06:55.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANO] She's always
the first one</b></Default>

00:06:55.160 --> 00:06:56.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to do things that people think</b></Default>

00:06:56.790 --> 00:06:59.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"I wish someone else
would do this."</b></Default>

00:06:59.910 --> 00:07:02.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why everyone says
she's amazing.</b></Default>

00:07:02.370 --> 00:07:05.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess that means Akagi had
a fulfilling high school life</b></Default>

00:07:05.540 --> 00:07:07.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-am I right?
-[sighs]</b></Default>

00:07:08.910 --> 00:07:09.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Am I wrong?</b></Default>

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:12.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can only tell you
about the rumors I've heard.</b></Default>

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But is that okay?</b></Default>

00:07:14.660 --> 00:07:16.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:07:24.160 --> 00:07:25.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Want some?</b></Default>

00:07:25.329 --> 00:07:26.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure, I'll have some.</b></Default>

00:07:28.910 --> 00:07:30.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Were you able
to check in with Akagi?</b></Default>

00:07:31.290 --> 00:07:32.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did.</b></Default>

00:07:32.290 --> 00:07:34.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Apparently, back in high school</b></Default>

00:07:34.079 --> 00:07:35.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi had a boyfriend
who was older</b></Default>

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:38.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she'd commute to school
from his place every day.</b></Default>

00:07:38.790 --> 00:07:40.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Story is</b></Default>

00:07:40.620 --> 00:07:42.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and was called to
the counselor's office</b></Default>

00:07:42.750 --> 00:07:44.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>multiple times
throughout the year.</b></Default>

00:07:44.620 --> 00:07:46.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you hear that story
from her directly?</b></Default>

00:07:46.949 --> 00:07:50.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. I was told
that it's only a rumor.</b></Default>

00:07:50.699 --> 00:07:51.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's pretty different</b></Default>

00:07:52.040 --> 00:07:54.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the way you described Akagi
to me the other day.</b></Default>

00:07:55.040 --> 00:07:56.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:07:56.120 --> 00:07:59.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now I think I understand her
even less than I did before.</b></Default>

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NOVEMBER 7TH</b></Default>

00:08:01.370 --> 00:08:02.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>YOKOHAMA INSTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY</b></Default>

00:08:06.500 --> 00:08:09.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] That's the one
for your university, right?</b></Default>

00:08:09.160 --> 00:08:11.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You taking
the entrance exams again?</b></Default>

00:08:11.079 --> 00:08:12.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My cram school student is.</b></Default>

00:08:12.790 --> 00:08:15.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would that student
happen to be the underclassmen</b></Default>

00:08:15.410 --> 00:08:16.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that Kunimi was talking about?</b></Default>

00:08:17.040 --> 00:08:19.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right. Toranosuke Kasai.</b></Default>

00:08:19.500 --> 00:08:21.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you ask why he's applying?</b></Default>

00:08:21.790 --> 00:08:23.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said he felt like it.</b></Default>

00:08:23.370 --> 00:08:24.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

00:08:25.660 --> 00:08:27.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, in our society</b></Default>

00:08:27.870 --> 00:08:30.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's a common theory
that poltergeists are caused</b></Default>

00:08:30.540 --> 00:08:32.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by unstable emotions
during puberty.</b></Default>

00:08:32.659 --> 00:08:34.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that means puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:08:34.409 --> 00:08:36.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has existed
in every generation, huh?</b></Default>

00:08:36.409 --> 00:08:37.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I can't say much</b></Default>

00:08:37.750 --> 00:08:39.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the information
you just shared.</b></Default>

00:08:39.750 --> 00:08:41.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are too many
vague elements.</b></Default>

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but the physical anomalies
are closest to Kaede's case</b></Default>

00:08:45.330 --> 00:08:46.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>don't you think?</b></Default>

00:08:46.370 --> 00:08:48.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not like
there are any scars</b></Default>

00:08:48.250 --> 00:08:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>left behind on her body</b></Default>

00:08:50.120 --> 00:08:51.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>On her back.</b></Default>

00:08:51.750 --> 00:08:53.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There were some claw marks</b></Default>

00:08:53.409 --> 00:08:55.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like she had scratched
around her shoulder blades.</b></Default>

00:08:56.409 --> 00:08:57.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You saw that?</b></Default>

00:08:57.789 --> 00:08:59.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I helped her get undressed.</b></Default>

00:09:01.039 --> 00:09:03.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just unzipped the back zipper
on her dress., okay?</b></Default>

00:09:03.909 --> 00:09:06.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really? Can you tell
Sakurajima that too?</b></Default>

00:09:06.789 --> 00:09:08.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please keep it a secret for me?</b></Default>

00:09:10.830 --> 00:09:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on. I'd really like
a response here, you know?</b></Default>

00:09:14.409 --> 00:09:15.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:09:15.870 --> 00:09:19.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If even you can't figure it out</b></Default>

00:09:19.289 --> 00:09:22.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although, if there really are
no lies in her stories</b></Default>

00:09:22.500 --> 00:09:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there is one thing
I can surmise from all of this.</b></Default>

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:26.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, and what's that?</b></Default>

00:09:26.539 --> 00:09:27.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's very unlike you.</b></Default>

00:09:27.950 --> 00:09:29.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You still haven't noticed?</b></Default>

00:09:29.539 --> 00:09:30.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Noticed what?</b></Default>

00:09:30.539 --> 00:09:33.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That girl was in love
with you, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:09:33.330 --> 00:09:35.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And she wants to
forget about it.</b></Default>

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:37.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But nothing's ever happened
between me and Akagi.</b></Default>

00:09:37.870 --> 00:09:39.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hear there are
some girls in this world</b></Default>

00:09:40.039 --> 00:09:42.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that will fall head over heels
over one Choco-Cornet.</b></Default>

00:09:42.950 --> 00:09:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's awfully convincing
coming from you, Futaba.</b></Default>

00:09:45.580 --> 00:09:48.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would suggest you hurry up
and remember for her already</b></Default>

00:09:48.789 --> 00:09:51.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before her ghost
comes after you.</b></Default>

00:09:51.159 --> 00:09:52.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

00:09:53.289 --> 00:09:54.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[keyboard tapping]</b></Default>

00:09:57.120 --> 00:10:01.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>#DREAMING</b></Default>

00:10:03.700 --> 00:10:04.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:10:05.500 --> 00:10:07.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NOVEMBER 8TH</b></Default>

00:10:08.370 --> 00:10:09.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello and welcome.</b></Default>

00:10:10.289 --> 00:10:11.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can sit wherever you'd like.</b></Default>

00:10:14.120 --> 00:10:15.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] By the way, Koga.</b></Default>

00:10:15.539 --> 00:10:16.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's up?</b></Default>

00:10:16.659 --> 00:10:19.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know about that
Dreaming tag thing, don't you?</b></Default>

00:10:19.330 --> 00:10:20.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, isn't that a bit old?</b></Default>

00:10:20.950 --> 00:10:22.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As an expert
in seeing the future</b></Default>

00:10:23.039 --> 00:10:24.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what do you think?</b></Default>

00:10:25.450 --> 00:10:28.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm. I have
a pretty bad feeling about it.</b></Default>

00:10:28.250 --> 00:10:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does that mean
you experienced it as well?</b></Default>

00:10:31.080 --> 00:10:32.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, it wasn't me.</b></Default>

00:10:32.409 --> 00:10:34.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But one of Nana's dreams
became reality.</b></Default>

00:10:34.789 --> 00:10:36.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was this one
where a boy and his friends</b></Default>

00:10:37.080 --> 00:10:39.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-approached me at the beach.
-And then?</b></Default>

00:10:39.700 --> 00:10:41.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the end</b></Default>

00:10:41.830 --> 00:10:42.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:10:42.830 --> 00:10:45.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was just some guy who Nana
went to middle school with.</b></Default>

00:10:45.789 --> 00:10:48.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was it shocking Yoneyama managed
to get a date before you?</b></Default>

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:51.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?
No, that isn't the case at all.</b></Default>

00:10:51.289 --> 00:10:52.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just don't rush yourself</b></Default>

00:10:52.620 --> 00:10:54.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and go out
with some weird guy, okay?</b></Default>

00:10:54.659 --> 00:10:56.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh... Huh?</b></Default>

00:10:56.659 --> 00:10:58.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's this, Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:10:58.120 --> 00:10:59.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'Grats on your acceptance.</b></Default>

00:10:59.750 --> 00:11:02.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I still haven't been
accepted yet, though.</b></Default>

00:11:02.200 --> 00:11:03.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You applied
for priority admission</b></Default>

00:11:04.039 --> 00:11:06.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-through school rec, right?
-Well, yeah, but--</b></Default>

00:11:06.500 --> 00:11:08.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then if you already have
the recommendation</b></Default>

00:11:08.830 --> 00:11:10.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are you planning
to invalidate it?</b></Default>

00:11:10.700 --> 00:11:12.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, of course I'm not!</b></Default>

00:11:12.330 --> 00:11:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, then that makes you
a certified college girl, Koga.</b></Default>

00:11:15.330 --> 00:11:16.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

00:11:16.950 --> 00:11:18.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I open it?</b></Default>

00:11:18.700 --> 00:11:21.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[squeals]
I've been wanting these!</b></Default>

00:11:21.250 --> 00:11:23.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Were they expensive?</b></Default>

00:11:23.080 --> 00:11:25.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I talked to Zukki
and she gave me a pair.</b></Default>

00:11:25.450 --> 00:11:27.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She told me
she received some extra ones.</b></Default>

00:11:27.620 --> 00:11:30.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told her it was a friend's
college acceptance gift.</b></Default>

00:11:30.409 --> 00:11:32.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks so much, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:11:35.450 --> 00:11:36.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ms. Tomobe.</b></Default>

00:11:36.789 --> 00:11:39.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta. It's been a while.</b></Default>

00:11:39.539 --> 00:11:41.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you come over to see
how Kaede is doing?</b></Default>

00:11:41.830 --> 00:11:43.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was in the area, so why not?</b></Default>

00:11:45.539 --> 00:11:47.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whenever I see Kaede</b></Default>

00:11:47.080 --> 00:11:49.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I find myself
being cheered up as well.</b></Default>

00:11:49.580 --> 00:11:51.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, it's all
thanks to you, ma'am.</b></Default>

00:11:52.039 --> 00:11:53.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How is university going, Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:11:54.080 --> 00:11:56.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, you know</b></Default>

00:11:57.500 --> 00:11:58.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way</b></Default>

00:11:58.580 --> 00:12:00.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>have you seen Ms. Akagi
on campus?</b></Default>

00:12:00.620 --> 00:12:01.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:12:01.750 --> 00:12:03.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, Ms. Tomobe</b></Default>

00:12:03.159 --> 00:12:04.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why do you know about Akagi?</b></Default>

00:12:05.950 --> 00:12:07.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It hasn't been that long</b></Default>

00:12:07.500 --> 00:12:09.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since I first
got to know Akagi.</b></Default>

00:12:09.750 --> 00:12:12.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But she's a very serious
and smart girl.</b></Default>

00:12:12.409 --> 00:12:14.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder
if she actually realizes</b></Default>

00:12:14.500 --> 00:12:17.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there are other people
who see her in that light.</b></Default>

00:12:17.159 --> 00:12:18.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know.</b></Default>

00:12:18.539 --> 00:12:21.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's like she seems
to find a sense of satisfaction</b></Default>

00:12:21.250 --> 00:12:22.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>being that way.</b></Default>

00:12:22.330 --> 00:12:25.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since she created
her volunteer group last month</b></Default>

00:12:25.159 --> 00:12:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been coming by to help out
whenever I'm able to</b></Default>

00:12:28.080 --> 00:12:29.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and during my time there</b></Default>

00:12:29.539 --> 00:12:32.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard about what
middle school she attended.</b></Default>

00:12:32.200 --> 00:12:35.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did Akagi say anything about me?</b></Default>

00:12:35.159 --> 00:12:37.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did something happen
between you two?</b></Default>

00:12:37.289 --> 00:12:39.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, not really.</b></Default>

00:12:39.580 --> 00:12:41.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I was told
by one of Akagi's friends</b></Default>

00:12:41.750 --> 00:12:44.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she's been acting
a bit out of character lately.</b></Default>

00:12:44.539 --> 00:12:46.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If Akagi was worried
about something</b></Default>

00:12:46.830 --> 00:12:48.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what do you think it could be?</b></Default>

00:12:48.620 --> 00:12:50.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, if I really had to guess</b></Default>

00:12:51.000 --> 00:12:53.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>being in love with someone</b></Default>

00:12:53.370 --> 00:12:55.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs] Can you think
of anything else?</b></Default>

00:12:56.000 --> 00:12:58.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh. What else? Let's see.</b></Default>

00:12:58.370 --> 00:12:59.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

00:12:59.909 --> 00:13:03.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe she just didn't want
to see you after what happened.</b></Default>

00:13:05.539 --> 00:13:08.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think the fact that
she wasn't able to save you</b></Default>

00:13:08.289 --> 00:13:12.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was possibly the biggest setback
Akagi has ever faced.</b></Default>

00:13:12.200 --> 00:13:13.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps she still regrets that</b></Default>

00:13:14.039 --> 00:13:16.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and carries those feelings
to this day.</b></Default>

00:13:17.500 --> 00:13:19.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, Ms. Tomobe...</b></Default>

00:13:19.370 --> 00:13:20.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:13:20.500 --> 00:13:22.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a favor I'd like to ask.</b></Default>

00:13:23.000 --> 00:13:24.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:13:25.039 --> 00:13:26.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NOVEMBER 12TH</b></Default>

00:13:26.580 --> 00:13:28.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL] Bye, Ms. Ikumi.
See you next time.</b></Default>

00:13:29.120 --> 00:13:30.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Take care.</b></Default>

00:13:30.539 --> 00:13:31.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[receding footsteps]</b></Default>

00:13:32.580 --> 00:13:33.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:13:33.909 --> 00:13:36.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must be upset the tour
request was from Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:13:37.370 --> 00:13:39.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry I kept it from you.</b></Default>

00:13:39.159 --> 00:13:42.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. Don't worry, Ms. Tomobe.
You did nothing wrong.</b></Default>

00:13:42.580 --> 00:13:43.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

00:13:43.870 --> 00:13:46.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will you two be okay
if I leave you alone here?</b></Default>

00:13:46.330 --> 00:13:49.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. Thank you again
for everything today.</b></Default>

00:13:49.409 --> 00:13:50.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOMOBE] See you next week.</b></Default>

00:13:50.950 --> 00:13:52.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[receding footsteps]</b></Default>

00:13:58.200 --> 00:13:59.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi, are you angry?</b></Default>

00:14:00.620 --> 00:14:03.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] We are in the middle
of a contest, are we not?</b></Default>

00:14:03.620 --> 00:14:06.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you keep showing up
around me like this</b></Default>

00:14:06.370 --> 00:14:08.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then I won't ever
be able to forget you.</b></Default>

00:14:11.039 --> 00:14:12.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You got something after this?</b></Default>

00:14:13.500 --> 00:14:16.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You sure have sharp eyes</b></Default>

00:14:16.120 --> 00:14:19.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you heading to Yokosuka
to protect the lost little girl</b></Default>

00:14:19.289 --> 00:14:21.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or are you gonna stop
the train accident?</b></Default>

00:14:21.700 --> 00:14:24.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, and there's a stolen bike
out there, too, right?</b></Default>

00:14:25.080 --> 00:14:26.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you looked it up.</b></Default>

00:14:26.450 --> 00:14:27.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be realistic.</b></Default>

00:14:27.789 --> 00:14:29.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't go after all of them.</b></Default>

00:14:31.330 --> 00:14:33.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How many more people
do you need to save</b></Default>

00:14:33.500 --> 00:14:35.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before your regrets fade away?</b></Default>

00:14:37.830 --> 00:14:39.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you... remember?</b></Default>

00:14:40.039 --> 00:14:42.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was thinking
you might be regretting</b></Default>

00:14:42.080 --> 00:14:44.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how you couldn't save me
back in middle school</b></Default>

00:14:44.539 --> 00:14:46.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and are holding on
to that feeling to this day.</b></Default>

00:14:49.909 --> 00:14:51.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't...</b></Default>

00:14:51.789 --> 00:14:53.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

00:14:53.539 --> 00:14:55.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps, groans]</b></Default>

00:14:55.330 --> 00:14:57.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Akagi?</b></Default>

00:15:00.080 --> 00:15:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] Again...</b></Default>

00:15:01.830 --> 00:15:04.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's still early in the day.</b></Default>

00:15:05.620 --> 00:15:07.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi. Let me see.</b></Default>

00:15:09.039 --> 00:15:10.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>BE WARY OF HIM
YOU OKAY OVER THERE?</b></Default>

00:15:11.000 --> 00:15:12.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SORRY ABOUT THE SPRAIN</b></Default>

00:15:12.539 --> 00:15:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:15:19.659 --> 00:15:20.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let me go.</b></Default>

00:15:22.700 --> 00:15:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you get involved</b></Default>

00:15:26.370 --> 00:15:28.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So it's true. I am to blame.</b></Default>

00:15:29.500 --> 00:15:32.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps you also know what that
poltergeist is about as well.</b></Default>

00:15:32.950 --> 00:15:35.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I told you that</b></Default>

00:15:35.830 --> 00:15:36.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN] Ikumi.</b></Default>

00:15:41.370 --> 00:15:44.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I already told you</b></Default>

00:15:44.409 --> 00:15:47.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please. I was just hoping that
you'd hear me out this time.</b></Default>

00:15:47.909 --> 00:15:49.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have something to do
right now.</b></Default>

00:15:49.789 --> 00:15:50.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.</b></Default>

00:15:53.330 --> 00:15:54.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:15:57.289 --> 00:16:00.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. By chance</b></Default>

00:16:02.450 --> 00:16:04.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We were dating for about a year</b></Default>

00:16:04.120 --> 00:16:05.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>back when
she was in high school.</b></Default>

00:16:05.909 --> 00:16:07.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] You heard about me
from Akagi?</b></Default>

00:16:08.000 --> 00:16:10.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN] Yeah. She showed me
her school yearbook</b></Default>

00:16:10.450 --> 00:16:11.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when we were together.</b></Default>

00:16:11.700 --> 00:16:13.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She told me a bit of the story</b></Default>

00:16:13.330 --> 00:16:15.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about what happened in class
at that time.</b></Default>

00:16:15.909 --> 00:16:19.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know, she seemed to be
awfully worried about you.</b></Default>

00:16:19.159 --> 00:16:21.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why did the two of you break up?</b></Default>

00:16:21.750 --> 00:16:25.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, uh, I was so busy
trying to find a job last year.</b></Default>

00:16:25.330 --> 00:16:28.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't have enough in me
to be considerate to her.</b></Default>

00:16:28.330 --> 00:16:30.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I applied for 50 companies</b></Default>

00:16:30.289 --> 00:16:32.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I got rejected
by all of them.</b></Default>

00:16:32.750 --> 00:16:35.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And even through all of that</b></Default>

00:16:36.500 --> 00:16:39.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'd always come over</b></Default>

00:16:39.539 --> 00:16:42.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she'd iron the shirts
I'd wear to the interviews.</b></Default>

00:16:42.909 --> 00:16:44.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And when I left
for an interview</b></Default>

00:16:44.909 --> 00:16:47.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she never said, "Do your best."
Not even once.</b></Default>

00:16:47.950 --> 00:16:50.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess
she didn't want to pressure me.</b></Default>

00:16:50.620 --> 00:16:51.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That all sounds nice.</b></Default>

00:16:51.789 --> 00:16:54.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I'm not really getting
why you would break up.</b></Default>

00:16:55.659 --> 00:16:58.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was overcome with anxiety
and ended up feeling</b></Default>

00:16:58.500 --> 00:17:01.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a righteous person like Ikumi
was annoying.</b></Default>

00:17:01.200 --> 00:17:03.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before I knew it</b></Default>

00:17:03.370 --> 00:17:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and told her, "Would you
just leave me alone?"</b></Default>

00:17:05.869 --> 00:17:08.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow, that's
pretty crummy of you.</b></Default>

00:17:08.250 --> 00:17:09.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't disagree.</b></Default>

00:17:09.700 --> 00:17:12.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, so as her ex-boyfriend</b></Default>

00:17:12.160 --> 00:17:14.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why'd you decide to come see her
at this point in time?</b></Default>

00:17:15.500 --> 00:17:18.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I saw a post that
she had written on social media</b></Default>

00:17:18.160 --> 00:17:20.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she had a dream
where she was arrested</b></Default>

00:17:20.450 --> 00:17:22.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because of
a bodily injury incident.</b></Default>

00:17:22.660 --> 00:17:23.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi?</b></Default>

00:17:24.200 --> 00:17:25.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know the rumors, right?</b></Default>

00:17:25.789 --> 00:17:27.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That Dreaming tag thing.</b></Default>

00:17:27.539 --> 00:17:30.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After seeing this</b></Default>

00:17:30.289 --> 00:17:32.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It occurred to me
that leaving Ikumi alone</b></Default>

00:17:32.500 --> 00:17:33.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would be a bad idea</b></Default>

00:17:34.329 --> 00:17:36.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because she has a side of her</b></Default>

00:17:36.450 --> 00:17:38.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where she can
only support herself</b></Default>

00:17:38.329 --> 00:17:40.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by supporting someone else.</b></Default>

00:17:40.500 --> 00:17:43.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's not really something
adults would believe in.</b></Default>

00:17:43.500 --> 00:17:45.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you know
what date that'll happen?</b></Default>

00:17:46.500 --> 00:17:49.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. It says it'll be
on November 27th.</b></Default>

00:17:51.000 --> 00:17:53.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
{\i1}The middle school reunion.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:17:59.329 --> 00:18:01.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] What are you doing
at the university</b></Default>

00:18:01.619 --> 00:18:02.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on a Saturday?</b></Default>

00:18:06.079 --> 00:18:08.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me what you did to Akagi.</b></Default>

00:18:08.250 --> 00:18:11.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I did was
hand out presents to everyone.</b></Default>

00:18:11.160 --> 00:18:13.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Presents that they all
wished for themselves.</b></Default>

00:18:13.539 --> 00:18:16.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't know Santa Claus
also gifts people poltergeists.</b></Default>

00:18:17.039 --> 00:18:18.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Excuse me?</b></Default>

00:18:18.119 --> 00:18:20.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The nature of
Ms. Akagi's puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:18:20.450 --> 00:18:21.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is nothing of the sort.</b></Default>

00:18:21.700 --> 00:18:24.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>#Dreaming. I'm guessing
that's your idea as well.</b></Default>

00:18:25.000 --> 00:18:27.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I could say
everyone gets worried</b></Default>

00:18:27.119 --> 00:18:28.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about their futures, don't they?</b></Default>

00:18:28.869 --> 00:18:31.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that's why you show them
their futures in their dreams.</b></Default>

00:18:31.910 --> 00:18:33.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not as though
I showed them myself.</b></Default>

00:18:34.039 --> 00:18:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're having those dreams
on their own accord.</b></Default>

00:18:36.579 --> 00:18:38.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Then one more thing.
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:18:38.700 --> 00:18:40.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you give me
your cell phone number?</b></Default>

00:18:40.869 --> 00:18:41.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

00:18:42.579 --> 00:18:45.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey. What subject
do you study at university?</b></Default>

00:18:45.700 --> 00:18:47.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Statistical science.</b></Default>

00:18:47.450 --> 00:18:49.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, then that
might be perfect.</b></Default>

00:18:49.329 --> 00:18:52.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're a STEM type</b></Default>

00:18:52.200 --> 00:18:54.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh?
-Three, two, one</b></Default>

00:18:54.700 --> 00:18:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>zero. [chuckles]</b></Default>

00:18:56.369 --> 00:18:57.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay. That's it.</b></Default>

00:18:57.619 --> 00:18:59.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could you please show me
one more time?</b></Default>

00:18:59.869 --> 00:19:02.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That chance
was the only one you get.</b></Default>

00:19:02.079 --> 00:19:04.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides, it looks like
we have company.</b></Default>

00:19:04.369 --> 00:19:05.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[approaching footsteps]</b></Default>

00:19:05.750 --> 00:19:07.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry for the wait.</b></Default>

00:19:07.250 --> 00:19:09.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai. Good work
on your supplemental class.</b></Default>

00:19:09.750 --> 00:19:13.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was a makeup class</b></Default>

00:19:13.160 --> 00:19:15.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, weren't you
just talking to someone?</b></Default>

00:19:15.700 --> 00:19:19.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, as you can see</b></Default>

00:19:20.500 --> 00:19:21.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] She was here?</b></Default>

00:19:21.789 --> 00:19:22.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:19:23.789 --> 00:19:26.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You saw Akagi, right?
How was she?</b></Default>

00:19:26.369 --> 00:19:29.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A lot happened</b></Default>

00:19:29.450 --> 00:19:30.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why is that?</b></Default>

00:19:30.579 --> 00:19:33.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly</b></Default>

00:19:33.160 --> 00:19:35.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can tell me on our way home.</b></Default>

00:19:35.079 --> 00:19:37.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, about that, actually</b></Default>

00:19:37.250 --> 00:19:40.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there's something about Akagi
that I wanna confirm first.</b></Default>

00:19:40.200 --> 00:19:42.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-So I'm gonna visit my parents.
-Okay, then.</b></Default>

00:19:42.700 --> 00:19:45.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can buy beaker puddings
at Yokohama Station.</b></Default>

00:19:45.250 --> 00:19:47.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? You wanna come with me?</b></Default>

00:19:47.579 --> 00:19:50.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I only visited them once
in the spring, after all.</b></Default>

00:19:50.289 --> 00:19:52.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, let's get going.</b></Default>

00:19:52.289 --> 00:19:53.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

00:19:54.500 --> 00:19:55.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Hello.</b></Default>

00:19:55.660 --> 00:19:57.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to intrude.</b></Default>

00:19:57.369 --> 00:19:59.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yes. Hello there.</b></Default>

00:19:59.950 --> 00:20:02.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, you didn't say
Mai was with you.</b></Default>

00:20:02.789 --> 00:20:04.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, dear?</b></Default>

00:20:04.750 --> 00:20:07.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Apologies for coming to visit
without notice.</b></Default>

00:20:07.289 --> 00:20:09.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, you're fine.
Welcome back, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:20:10.039 --> 00:20:11.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's good to see you.</b></Default>

00:20:11.539 --> 00:20:12.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And here's a souvenir.</b></Default>

00:20:13.250 --> 00:20:14.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. Thank you.</b></Default>

00:20:14.700 --> 00:20:16.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you two
gonna stay for dinner?</b></Default>

00:20:16.910 --> 00:20:19.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to make more main dishes
and reset the rice cooker.</b></Default>

00:20:19.950 --> 00:20:21.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, we won't be long.</b></Default>

00:20:21.329 --> 00:20:23.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I'll help out.
-You will?</b></Default>

00:20:23.450 --> 00:20:25.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But are you sure
that's all right?</b></Default>

00:20:25.700 --> 00:20:28.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like you to teach me
how you season food.</b></Default>

00:20:28.369 --> 00:20:29.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, my.</b></Default>

00:20:29.789 --> 00:20:33.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It almost feels as though Sakuta
has found himself a bride.</b></Default>

00:20:34.039 --> 00:20:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, Dad, do you remember
someone named Akagi?</b></Default>

00:20:37.829 --> 00:20:40.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We went to the same
middle school together.</b></Default>

00:20:40.160 --> 00:20:41.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I remember her.</b></Default>

00:20:42.119 --> 00:20:43.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I recall correctly</b></Default>

00:20:43.450 --> 00:20:46.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>her mother was one of
the executives in the PTA.</b></Default>

00:20:46.369 --> 00:20:49.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. I believe
she was a lawyer, wasn't she?</b></Default>

00:20:49.160 --> 00:20:52.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was impressive, juggling
all that alongside work.</b></Default>

00:20:52.119 --> 00:20:54.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But why do you
bring this up so suddenly?</b></Default>

00:20:54.660 --> 00:20:56.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She goes to our university.</b></Default>

00:20:56.619 --> 00:20:59.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I realized I didn't
remember her all that well</b></Default>

00:20:59.250 --> 00:21:01.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I was wondering
what she was like.</b></Default>

00:21:01.200 --> 00:21:03.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, then I might have
just the thing</b></Default>

00:21:03.200 --> 00:21:04.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to jog your memory.</b></Default>

00:21:04.579 --> 00:21:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm?</b></Default>

00:21:09.250 --> 00:21:10.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here, son.</b></Default>

00:21:11.200 --> 00:21:12.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why, this...</b></Default>

00:21:12.369 --> 00:21:15.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When we were pulling out
winter clothes, we found this.</b></Default>

00:21:15.250 --> 00:21:16.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The moving service noticed</b></Default>

00:21:16.700 --> 00:21:19.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it was in the trash
to throw out when we moved</b></Default>

00:21:19.200 --> 00:21:21.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and they kindly
brought it over to me.</b></Default>

00:21:22.329 --> 00:21:24.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ gentle music]</b></Default>

00:21:26.250 --> 00:21:27.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>CLASS 3-1</b></Default>

00:21:35.789 --> 00:21:37.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] {\i1}When I graduated{\i0}
{\i1}from grade school</b></Default>

00:21:38.079 --> 00:21:40.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I wrote in my graduation essay</b></Default>

00:21:40.160 --> 00:21:44.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}"I want to become an adult{\i0}
{\i1}that can be of help to others."{\i0}</b></Default>

00:21:44.160 --> 00:21:46.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}In my first year</b></Default>

00:21:46.660 --> 00:21:49.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}in preparing for and running{\i0}
{\i1}the sports festival{\i0}</b></Default>

00:21:49.119 --> 00:21:51.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}and cultural festival</b></Default>

00:21:51.250 --> 00:21:53.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}My favorite memories{\i0}
{\i1}of the second year{\i0}</b></Default>

00:21:53.289 --> 00:21:55.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}are definitely{\i0}
{\i1}of the student council.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:21:55.329 --> 00:21:58.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Student council work{\i0}
{\i1}as the secretary was new to me</b></Default>

00:21:58.079 --> 00:21:59.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}but felt worthwhile.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:21:59.660 --> 00:22:00.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}In my third year</b></Default>

00:22:00.950 --> 00:22:02.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I couldn't do anything at all.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:02.950 --> 00:22:04.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}That's why{\i0}
{\i1}in my high school years</b></Default>

00:22:04.910 --> 00:22:06.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I want to make sure{\i0}
{\i1}I become an adult{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:06.869 --> 00:22:08.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}that can be of help to others.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:08.789 --> 00:22:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So Akagi's
biggest regret from back then</b></Default>

00:22:11.619 --> 00:22:13.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>really was that
she couldn't save me.</b></Default>

00:22:15.750 --> 00:22:19.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MEMORIES OF MIDDLE SCHOOL LIFE
CLASS 3-1, SAKUTA AZUSAGAWA</b></Default>

00:22:19.910 --> 00:22:21.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft gasp]</b></Default>

00:22:21.539 --> 00:22:23.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] {\i1}Do you remember{\i0}
{\i1}what you wrote{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:23.539 --> 00:22:25.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}for your graduation essay{\i0}
{\i1}in middle school?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:26.450 --> 00:22:27.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean</b></Default>

00:22:27.910 --> 00:22:31.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you wrote "Someday, I think
I'd like to reach kindness."</b></Default>

00:22:31.500 --> 00:22:34.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I didn't write
anything of the sort in here.</b></Default>

00:22:34.539 --> 00:22:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here's what I think, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:22:36.619 --> 00:22:40.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Life's purpose is to help us
learn to become kinder.</b></Default>

00:22:41.039 --> 00:22:43.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}Those were words{\i0}
{\i1}that I heard from Shoko-san.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:43.829 --> 00:22:44.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}But back then</b></Default>

00:22:45.039 --> 00:22:46.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I hadn't clearly{\i0}
{\i1}remembered the fact{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:46.950 --> 00:22:48.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}that I had even met her yet.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:48.539 --> 00:22:50.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}So there's no way{\i0}
{\i1}I could write that.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:51.079 --> 00:22:53.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could she have, perhaps...</b></Default>

00:22:55.500 --> 00:22:57.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ closing theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:22:57.619 --> 00:23:03.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF A NIGHTINGALE</b></Default>

00:23:56.000 --> 00:23:59.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:23:59.329 --> 00:24:01.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NEXT EPISODE
#7 FROM BEYOND HILBERT SPACE</b></Default>
